{"tid":1677120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Remember remember, the 5th of November. 11月5日 18區 V煞營火晚會！","createTime":"2019-10-27T01:39:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T06:00:34.000Z","uid":238101,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b9e5c9c20b2d5059b356f2f8b29084b24d13ca39","tid":1677120,"uid":238101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T01:39:54.000Z","msg":"V煞面具代表反極權係人都知，咁你知唔知佢成日講既 Remember remember the 5th of November 有咩咁特別？<br />\n<br />\n一切源於個面具上既人，呢個人唔係V for Vendetta ，戴個個先係。面具上既人叫 Guy Fawkes。佢係1605 年反英組織既成員。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yG17gXY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyG17gXY.jpg&h=ef7c5f50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGuy Fawkes 策劃11月5日炸爆當時既英國國會，但係計劃實行既幾小時前，比警察係國會既地底捉到正，最後炸唔成，仲因為叛國罪被判死刑。佢唔想死得太痛苦，係吊刑台跳落去仆死左。<br />\n<br />\n呢個炸國會失敗既故事，即係英國人民既勝利，所以自此每年11月5日，都有大型營火晚會黎慶祝當時處決左呢個叛國者。呢晚就係Guy Fawkes Night，又叫Bonfire Night 營火日，大家睇下每年既晚會有幾熱烈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PCNN1rR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPCNN1rR.jpg&h=61f922c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oj7ioFc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foj7ioFc.jpg&h=2373c661&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XkeHQkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXkeHQkd.jpg&h=a8edbb72&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/et7Kjdz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fet7Kjdz.jpg&h=488fcbe7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Abxuvkf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAbxuvkf.jpg&h=7971876b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無錯！Guy Fawkes比人喻為失敗者左兩個世紀！但係V for Vendetta 既故事入面，主角繼承Guy Fawkes既遺願，戴上佢個樣既面具，炸爆左英國國會，仲係11月5日令全民變V。 Guy Fawkes由失敗者，變左做反極權既象徵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n故仔講完。唔知有幾多人想11月5日一齊舉行呢個英國傳統節日？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人都抖左咁耐，捱左咁耐，係時候沖沖喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">11月5晚18區V煞營火晚會</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">面具之下 理念不毀</span>"},{"pid":"c3218163250663c0fdb627ea4005294e10d4caca","tid":1677120,"uid":238101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T01:41:43.000Z","msg":"今日尖咀見<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EWwfqWL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEWwfqWL.jpg&h=7d643dd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1954afd22e2b14dae0758fd05ff74665233a80f6","tid":1677120,"uid":238101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T01:42:19.000Z","msg":"P牌無力推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ab67c18123650ddd600255a0dea077410652f35","tid":1677120,"uid":238101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T01:43:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6wfqXy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6wfqXy.png&h=979c102d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NmKdcCz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNmKdcCz.jpg&h=d7e05724&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3b81662eef349553225e2706adec94ec920bdee2","tid":1677120,"uid":238101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T01:51:04.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 認真行動po無人理"},{"pid":"20d99ce69a2e8627fe3530e236d9fa5a9429312c","tid":1677120,"uid":58803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T03:21:14.000Z","msg":"營火晚會？即係11月5一齊燒左